Drama series based on the acclaimed US show.
When the bones of young Tommy Keegan are
discovered in a basement, DS Ronnie Brooks, DS
Matt Devlin and DI Natalie Chandler are faced
with a 20-year-old cold case. The only people
who seem to know anything about the case are
the man originally arrested after the boy's
disappearance, and Tommy's best friend Julia,
who may have repressed memories. Crown
Prosecutors Alesha Phillips and James Steel
have a risky case on their hands.
